description: Explore infinite realms, collect and breed spirits, engage in action combat, and build your own realm in this multiplayer adventure.
instructions: To complete setup: 1) Open Roblox Studio, 2) File > Publish to Roblox As, 3) Create experience with name above, 4) Replace PLACEHOLDER values with actual IDs from Studio Home tab, 5) Run: node update-rojo-config.js
